snippet.title: The Last Son of Krypton - Rebuilding The Snyderverse #2
snippet.description:
Welcome back to Rebuilding the Snyderverse. This is the web series where we will be rebuilding the Snyderverse using the current DCEU as well as adding new stories to it. This is episode 2 and today we will be discussing the first new addition to the Snyderverse which will be a Superman HBOMAX series set in between Man of Steel and Batman v Superman.
